1
00:00:02,268 --> 00:00:03,269
Hey, bro.

2
00:00:04,270 --> 00:00:05,605
I've got something to tell you.

3
00:00:06,006 --> 00:00:07,474
Hei Yan and I are together.

4
00:00:09,242 --> 00:00:11,444
Together? Since when?

5
00:00:13,413 --> 00:00:15,181
It's been over ten years.

6
00:00:17,183 --> 00:00:18,484
Over ten years?

7
00:00:18,485 --> 00:00:19,885
You've been together for ten years?

8
00:00:20,380 --> 00:00:22,020
I mean, we've known each other that long.

9
00:00:22,322 --> 00:00:24,090
We've actually been together...

10
00:00:26,092 --> 00:00:27,260
for two days.

11
00:00:29,863 --> 00:00:30,863
Together.

12
00:00:31,264 --> 00:00:32,984
How could you have known him for ten years?

13
00:00:34,000 --> 00:00:34,901
Remember back then,

14
00:00:34,902 --> 00:00:36,669
when Dad sent me to that foundation?

15
00:00:37,170 --> 00:00:38,872
I told you about that study buddy, right?

16
00:00:41,941 --> 00:00:44,544
That's when you met?
You were talking to him every day.

17
00:00:45,378 --> 00:00:46,112
It was like an online romance.

18
00:00:46,113 --> 00:00:47,913
The family thought you were in trouble.

19
00:00:47,914 --> 00:00:49,181
Then he vanished.

20
00:00:49,182 --> 00:00:50,582
And didn't you swear

21
00:00:50,583 --> 00:00:51,351
that he'd better never show his face

22
00:00:51,352 --> 00:00:52,552
on this planet again?

23
00:00:55,221 --> 00:00:56,489
Well, he's Hei Mingyan.

24
00:00:59,325 --> 00:01:00,460
Who's Hei Mingyan?

25
00:01:01,895 --> 00:01:02,629
Hei Mingyan...

26
00:01:02,630 --> 00:01:04,264
is Hei Yan's real name.

27
00:01:05,632 --> 00:01:08,201
He cut contact so he wouldn't hold me back.

28
00:01:08,501 --> 00:01:09,803
He joined the industry

29
00:01:10,170 --> 00:01:11,671
just to get closer to me.

30
00:01:12,739 --> 00:01:14,373
He even arranged this collaboration

31
00:01:14,374 --> 00:01:15,742
as a way to remember us.

32
00:01:16,843 --> 00:01:17,843
Even his stage name

33
00:01:17,844 --> 00:01:19,411
was chosen because of me.

34
00:01:19,412 --> 00:01:20,813
He wanted me to have

35
00:01:20,814 --> 00:01:22,915
smooth sailing in life.

36
00:01:22,916 --> 00:01:24,451
That's so romantic.

37
00:01:25,727 --> 00:01:27,654
You really are quick to take his side.

38
00:01:28,221 --> 00:01:29,022
Just the other day, you were saying

39
00:01:29,023 --> 00:01:30,456
how heartless Hei Yan was.

40
00:01:30,457 --> 00:01:31,791
Now look at you, all starry-eyed.

41
00:01:32,091 --> 00:01:34,394
It's so romantic.

42
00:01:34,894 --> 00:01:35,994
Listen to me.

43
00:01:35,995 --> 00:01:36,496
Keep this relationship

44
00:01:36,497 --> 00:01:37,764
under wraps for now.

45
00:01:38,031 --> 00:01:39,698
We have nothing to hide.

46
00:01:39,699 --> 00:01:40,899
Why should we?

47
00:01:40,900 --> 00:01:42,936
It'll be a mess for me if you break up.

48
00:01:43,303 --> 00:01:44,804
That's not going to happen.

49
00:01:45,171 --> 00:01:46,506
Even if it doesn't,

50
00:01:46,773 --> 00:01:47,841
there's still your father.

51
00:01:48,141 --> 00:01:49,042
My dad?

52
00:01:49,043 --> 00:01:50,876
He can't stop me.

53
00:01:50,877 --> 00:01:52,845
He'll just be pissed off at first.

54
00:01:52,846 --> 00:01:53,813
Then,

55
00:01:53,814 --> 00:01:55,094
he'll start acting all pathetic.

56
00:01:55,415 --> 00:01:56,415
And in the end,

57
00:01:57,450 --> 00:01:58,730
he'll just have to deal with it.

58
00:01:59,018 --> 00:01:59,919
Fine.

59
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,521
But what about Hei Yan's family?

60
00:02:01,754 --> 00:02:04,090
He doesn't have any family left.

61
00:02:05,658 --> 00:02:06,926
What about Lin Bingchen?

62
00:02:08,094 --> 00:02:09,194
Lin Bingchen?

63
00:02:09,195 --> 00:02:10,195
Yeah.

64
00:02:10,296 --> 00:02:11,631
Exactly, Lin Bingchen.

65
00:02:12,198 --> 00:02:13,265
It's because you

66
00:02:13,266 --> 00:02:14,834
don't get along with Lin Bingchen

67
00:02:15,201 --> 00:02:16,668
that we're being

68
00:02:16,669 --> 00:02:18,137
forced apart like this.

69
00:02:18,138 --> 00:02:19,305
This is on you.

70
00:02:21,574 --> 00:02:23,309
Those PR samples that came in are great.

71
00:02:25,612 --> 00:02:27,412
The tie and the silk scarf

72
00:02:27,413 --> 00:02:28,547
will be perfect for the next event.

73
00:02:28,548 --> 00:02:30,282
Make sure you use them.
OK?

74
00:02:30,717 --> 00:02:31,484
And remember to tag them.

75
00:02:31,484 --> 00:02:32,484
Don't forget, okay?

76
00:02:34,587 --> 00:02:35,088
I'll go ahead and

77
00:02:35,089 --> 00:02:36,209
put them on your nightstand.

78
00:02:36,890 --> 00:02:38,170
I'm putting them in the cabinet,

79
00:02:38,258 --> 00:02:39,492
so don't forget they're there.

80
00:02:43,930 --> 00:02:45,464
It's all because of you and Lin Bingchen.

81
00:02:45,465 --> 00:02:46,699
You two just can't get along.
